      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a reliable friend on the road. It\u2019s in really great shape and drives like a dream\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable ride that\u2019s been well-loved and properly cared for. It\u2019s super clean, runs smoothly, and is totally ready for your next road trip! I'm sad to see it go, but I know you're going to love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
