    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a prime example of high-revving, naturally aspirated performance, powered by the S65 4.0L V8 featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. The power is managed by a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a Variable M Differential Lock for optimal longitudinal and lateral dynamics. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity with M-specific suspension geometry and hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering for uncompromised tactile feedback. Key preventative maintenance, including rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacement, has been performed to ensure the longevity of the S65's reciprocating assembly. While the vehicle shows minor signs of road use consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain remains tight and the power delivery is linear and aggressive.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
