    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 BMW 540i xDrive is an exceptional find for a driver seeking a balance of executive luxury and athletic performance. The Bluestone Metallic exterior remains vibrant, showing only minor, typical stone chips on the front fascia that are barely visible from a distance. Inside, the Black Dakota leather seats are supple and free of tears, with the cabin retaining that signature premium scent. All electronics, including the Harman Kardon surround sound and the gesture-control infotainment system, function perfectly. Under the hood, the 3.0L turbocharged inline-six runs smoothly, backed by a comprehensive service history detailing every oil change and a recent spark plug replacement. The 19-inch M Sport wheels are wrapped in tires with plenty of tread remaining. This is a well-maintained, smoke-free vehicle that delivers a tight, responsive ride without any rattles or mechanical concerns. It is truly turn-key and ready for its next long-distance cruise or daily commute.",
